title: Ralph Guerra (comedian)
description: This week we're closing out 2015 with comedian and proprietor of http://www.racingjunk.com/ Ralph Guerra (@RalphComedy). Ralph arrives in his newly purchased Taurus SHO, we talk a bit about RacingJunk, cover Netflix binging on Making a Murderer, Matt gets the Mustang back from its latest round of repairs, I give up a little info on what the Mosler Twinstar was actually like and Ralph shares stories about doing bad standup in strip clubs.
author: matt@thesmokingtire.com (Matt Farah & Zack Klapman)
